    <div class="main review-item" id="1004627">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1004627/" class="title-link">挑战与应战</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1004627"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/celadevra/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1018680-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/celadevra/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">徐栖</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2005-09-10"
      class="main-meta">2005-09-10 22:28:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1004627_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本书是阿诺德·汤因比在完成他的12卷巨著《历史研究》后，根据读者的意见缩写的版本。我没有读过12卷版，但粗读了一遍这本书后，觉得即使只是这样一个缩写版本也体现了世界历史的脉络，而且基本阐释清楚了汤因比的挑战与应战理论。如果不是专业研究历史但对历史及史学感兴趣...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1004627/#comments">(9回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">53有用 / 1没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            上海人民出版社2000版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
